{"tid":1356422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合次要敵人 （其他鄉紳、如劉業強），打擊主要敵人（鄉黑何君堯）","createTime":"2019-07-23T13:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T13:36:31.000Z","uid":42799,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a332a5259ca8dbdd71248344f1a48b346938e20c","tid":1356422,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:27:34.000Z","msg":"727 元朗勢在必行，希望各位手足以智行事避免受傷。<br />\n<br />\n焦點應放在警黑合作，聯合次要敵人 （其他鄉紳、如劉業強），打擊主要敵人（鄉黑何君堯警賊）。強如英治政府同港共政府都唔敢搞鄉紳就知道鄉紳既勢力相當大。<br />\n<br />\n利用群眾（其他鄉紳，既得利益）鬥群眾 （新進中共扶持既鄉黑），令到警賊中共為左處理鄉土問題更加疲於奔命。"},{"pid":"ac8b36e061fabfdef268d9f6d4603fc1bce7e9da","tid":1356422,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a8f0be06724c999f58ec37073b4f81f30b47f45","tid":1356422,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:28:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b09b74d8adc82b07a40d044783137e4b04cbd010","tid":1356422,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:28:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b28cc0b5010a2dd03a42162057a8e0508d8a6b71","tid":1356422,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:28:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f97d48f2ed17b0243986bace26d3eaec7324841d","tid":1356422,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:28:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b53dffe6cb8c44faf9683955fe949db7ddeb4d69","tid":1356422,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:28:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30182880922cb25439f8f32fc6be91e70e05921a","tid":1356422,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02bf670f57be9f6208c9fdece9be647f5bb040f4","tid":1356422,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:28:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89e497b1e0c896d7777d29c46e9cbaa91ceaf7ae","tid":1356422,"uid":427